snippet.title: Kim Raffo 35 - Molly Dilts 20 - Barbara Breidor 42 - Tracy Roberts 23
snippet.description:
#truecrime #coldcase  #newjersey4 #newjerseyfour 
"On Nov. 20, 2006, the four female victims were found behind the former Golden Key Motel in West Atlantic City (Egg Harbor Township). The drainage ditch runs parallel with Route 322 and contains fresh water run-off. It is five feet deep and 10 feet wide." - dailyvoice.com
